{"title": "Tactical Studies on the Battles around Plevna", "description": "Tactical Studies on the Battles around Plevna, or in German, Der Kampf um Plewna, examines with a critical eye the actions and engagements of the siege of Plevna (now Pleven in Bulgaria) during the Danube Campaign of the Russo-Turkish War of 1877-78. In doing so it offers a rare glimpse into the military art as practiced by the Imperial Russian army, and an unfiltered evaluation of it to German Imperial sensibilities.<br><br>\r\n\r\nFor an index of places relevant to the text, along with their modern names, click this <a href=\"https://archive.org/details/tactical-studies-companion-booklet\">hyperlink</a>. <br><br>\r\n\r\n-Summary by Alister<br>", "duration": 19662, "language": "English", "authors": [{"id": "17298", "name": "Thilo Lebrecht Ernst Michael von Trotha"}], "coverArt": null, "copyright_year": "1896", "genres": ["War & Military"], "supporters": [{"role": "Read by", "name": "Alister"}, {"role": "Book Coordinator", "name": "Alister"}, {"role": "Meta Coordinator", "name": "Rapunzelina"}], "sections": [{"section": 1, "title": "Part 1 - Introductory Review of the Danube Campaign", "readers": [17571], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/tacticalstudiesplevna_2301_librivox/tacticalstudiesplevna_01_trotha_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1314}, {"section": 2, "title": "Part 2 - Review of the Operations Around Plevna", "readers": [17571], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/tacticalstudiesplevna_2301_librivox/tacticalstudiesplevna_02_trotha_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1234}, {"section": 3, "title": "Part 3 - Plevna", "readers": [17571], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/tacticalstudiesplevna_2301_librivox/tacticalstudiesplevna_03_trotha_64kb.mp3", "duration": 679}, {"section": 4, "title": "Part 4 - The Action at Plevna on July 20th", "readers": [17571], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/tacticalstudiesplevna_2301_librivox/tacticalstudiesplevna_04_trotha_64kb.mp3", "duration": 91